Quest Details

Introduction

In this quest, we’ll be taking a look at some tools that a smart contract developer can make use of to be a more effective and efficient developer. Some of the tools we’ll be exploring include Solidity Metrics, cloc, as well as static analyzers like Slither.

📢 Note that there’ll be no rewards available for this quest, so feel free to take your time to thoroughly absorb all the information 🙂 Also, the content from this quest will be tested in our weekly Tuesday quiz on our Discord server.

For technical help on the StackUp platform & quest-related questions, join our Discord, head to the 🆘 | quest-help-forum channel and look for the correct thread to ask your question.
